ogle.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I&ll=30.543563%2C130.956797"},{"id":"d4w21umsb","geo":[30.54326,130.957282],"priority":110,"name":"フラウ宅（元ホテル）","isFolder":false,"mid":"1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I","image":"/images/points/37673/d4w21umsb_1695227467726.jpg","ep":4,"s":"","mark":"フラウが引っ越してくるホテル。廃墟なので中に入る事はできません。","density":63,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I&ll=30.54326%2C130.957282"},{"id":"d4w21unbe","geo":[30.540585,130.960614],"priority":29,"name":"中央種子島高校（種子島中央高等学校）","isFolder":false,"mid":"1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I","image":"/images/points/37673/d4w21unbe_1695200975023.jpg","ep":1,"s":"","mark":"「君島レポートNo.5」があった場所。ARアノテーションの位置は一番高い旗の天辺。ゲーム内では「中央種子島高校」。敷地内に入るには申請すれば行けますが、校舎内には入れません。「秒速5センチメートル」でも出てきた学校らしい。","density":33,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I&ll=30.540585%2C130.960614"},{"id":"d4w21un80","geo":[30.540863,130.960514],"priority":5,"name":"中央種子島高校：駐輪場","isFolder":false,"mid":"1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I","image":"/images/points/37673/d4w21un80_1695200987454.jpg","ep":1,"s":"","mark":"カイたちがバイクを停める場所。","density":33,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I&ll=30.540863%2C130.960514"},{"id":"d4w21unb8","geo":[30.540971,130.961781],"priority":8,"name":"中央種子島高校：昇降口","isFolder":false,"mid":"1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I","s":"","mark":"中には入れないのでゲームCGの通りの絵は撮れません。","density":53,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I&ll=30.540971%2C130.961781"},{"id":"d4w21umsg","geo":[30.541438,130.96187],"priority":5,"name":"中央種子島高校：渡り廊下","isFolder":false,"mid":"1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I","s":"","mark":"ジュンちゃんが漏らしそうになった場所。","density":53,"origin":"Google My Maps","originURL":"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1tiOp1zfOAc3gI-YbLWnIKlVCw_I&ll=30.541438%2C130.96187"}